00:31:49,923 --> 00:31:50,183
Thank you.

566
00:31:50,203 --> 00:31:50,563
Thank you.

567
00:31:50,623 --> 00:31:50,943
Thank you.

568
00:31:51,727 --> 00:31:56,952
and I love that, and very based around humans and what humans do and how they shape things.

