00:32:01,557 --> 00:32:07,702
is that he tends to have one core magic in his world that then manifests in multiple ways

571
00:32:08,383 --> 00:32:13,087
that the people in the world don't realize are the same thing, which is a really neat trick for

572
00:32:13,127 --> 00:32:16,671
building a sci-fi setting because it makes everything feel connected even though everything

573
00:32:16,731 --> 00:32:17,512
is also disparate.

574
00:32:17,909 --> 00:32:20,831
So you get a sense of wonder, but a sense that it all comes from the same,

