00:32:43,412 --> 00:32:47,934
If you want to kind of make your world compelling, especially if the player doesn't understand it and explore it

587
00:32:49,134 --> 00:32:55,997
But if you if you lay out the like lots of technological rules in the way that Star Trek does you end up with this

588
00:32:56,057 --> 00:33:02,840
Incredibly complicated world. It's very inaccessible for people coming into it new. So ideally what we have is two rules

589
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:05,541
with interesting consequences and

590
00:33:06,081 --> 00:33:11,023
So we try to do that. We try to make our world set up in a way that

591
00:33:13,803 --> 00:33:14,684
that would follow.

592
00:33:15,865 --> 00:33:21,530
Everything in the world comes from these two technological ideas that we had, which kind

