00:33:25,053 --> 00:33:27,395
in the narrative, and then you think, well, how can I express this narrative?

595
00:33:27,675 --> 00:33:31,779
And it all kind of twists around itself, and you bring in things which are interesting,

596
00:33:31,819 --> 00:33:36,042
and you cut them to the charm, and there was lots of research that kind of inspired various

