00:36:07,426 --> 00:36:09,268
because it helps you do something else, but

638
00:36:09,588 --> 00:36:12,931
how do you make sure you're not, like, falling down a rabbit hole when you're in a space like that?

639
00:36:14,092 --> 00:36:14,913
So, um...

