00:36:22,019 --> 00:36:24,681
possibly the same as designing games in general.

643
00:36:25,161 --> 00:36:28,965
That you have to think as a player, and then you also have to think as a creator.

644
00:36:28,985 --> 00:36:29,725
So you have to think...

645
00:36:30,261 --> 00:36:32,142
as a writer and you also have to think as a reader.

